      <title>Obsidian数学块语法</title>
      <link href="/2025/11/25/obsidian-shu-xue-kuai-yu-fa/"/>
      <url>/2025/11/25/obsidian-shu-xue-kuai-yu-fa/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="基本数学公式插入"><a href="#基本数学公式插入" class="headerlink" title="基本数学公式插入"></a>基本数学公式插入</h1><h2 id="行内公式"><a href="#行内公式" class="headerlink" title="行内公式"></a>行内公式</h2><p>使用单个美元符号 <code>$...$</code> 包裹公式：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一个行内公式 $E=mc^2$ 的例子。</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>效果：这是一个行内公式 $E=mc^2$ 的例子。</p><h2 id="块级公式"><a href="#块级公式" class="headerlink" title="块级公式"></a>块级公式</h2><p>使用双美元符号 <code>$$...$$</code> 包裹公式（单独一行）：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">\int<span class="emphasis">_a^b f(x)dx = F(b) - F(a)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">$$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>效果：<br>$$<br>\int_a^b f(x)dx = F(b) - F(a)<br>$$</p><h1 id="常用数学符号与表达式"><a href="#常用数学符号与表达式" class="headerlink" title="常用数学符号与表达式"></a>常用数学符号与表达式</h1><h2 id="希腊字母"><a href="#希腊字母" class="headerlink" title="希腊字母"></a>希腊字母</h2><table><thead><tr><th>符号</th><th>LaTeX 代码</th><th>符号</th><th>LaTeX 代码</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>α</td><td><code>\alpha</code></td><td>β</td><td><code>\beta</code></td></tr><tr><td>γ</td><td><code>\gamma</code></td><td>Γ</td><td><code>\Gamma</code></td></tr><tr><td>θ</td><td><code>\theta</code></td><td>Θ</td><td><code>\Theta</code></td></tr><tr><td>π</td><td><code>\pi</code></td><td>Π</td><td><code>\Pi</code></td></tr><tr><td>σ</td><td><code>\sigma</code></td><td>Σ</td><td><code>\Sigma</code></td></tr><tr><td>ω</td><td><code>\omega</code></td><td>Ω</td><td><code>\Omega</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="运算符"><a href="#运算符" class="headerlink" title="运算符"></a>运算符</h2><table><thead><tr><th>符号</th><th>LaTeX 代码</th><th>符号</th><th>LaTeX 代码</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>+</td><td><code>+</code></td><td>−</td><td><code>-</code></td></tr><tr><td>×</td><td><code>\times</code></td><td>÷</td><td><code>\div</code></td></tr><tr><td>±</td><td><code>\pm</code></td><td>∓</td><td><code>\mp</code></td></tr><tr><td>≤</td><td><code>\leq</code></td><td>≥</td><td><code>\geq</code></td></tr><tr><td>≠</td><td><code>\neq</code></td><td>≈</td><td><code>\approx</code></td></tr><tr><td>∈</td><td><code>\in</code></td><td>∉</td><td><code>\notin</code></td></tr><tr><td>∩</td><td><code>\cap</code></td><td>∪</td><td><code>\cup</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="关系符号"><a href="#关系符号" class="headerlink" title="关系符号"></a>关系符号</h2><table><thead><tr><th>语法</th><th>显示</th><th>语法</th><th>显示</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>\leq</code></td><td>$\leq$</td><td><code>\geq</code></td><td>$\geq$</td></tr><tr><td><code>\neq</code></td><td>$\neq$</td><td><code>\approx</code></td><td>$\approx$</td></tr><tr><td><code>\equiv</code></td><td>$\equiv$</td><td><code>\propto</code></td><td>$\propto$</td></tr><tr><td><code>\in</code></td><td>$\in$</td><td><code>\notin</code></td><td>$\notin$</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="空格处理"><a href="#空格处理" class="headerlink" title="空格处理"></a>空格处理</h2><p>LaTeX 默认会忽略空格，需要使用特定命令显示空格：</p><table><thead><tr><th>命令</th><th>空格大小</th><th>示例</th><th>效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>\,</code></td><td>小空格</td><td><code>$a\,b$</code></td><td>$a,b$</td></tr><tr><td><code>\:</code></td><td>中空格</td><td><code>$a\:b$</code></td><td>$a:b$</td></tr><tr><td><code>\;</code></td><td>大空格</td><td><code>$a\;b$</code></td><td>$a;b$</td></tr><tr><td><code>\quad</code></td><td>1em</td><td><code>$a\quad b$</code></td><td>$a\quad b$</td></tr><tr><td><code>\qquad</code></td><td>2em</td><td><code>$a\qquad b$</code></td><td>$a\qquad b$</td></tr><tr><td><code>\!</code></td><td>负空格</td><td><code>$a\!b$</code></td><td>$a!b$</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="求和、积分、极限"><a href="#求和、积分、极限" class="headerlink" title="求和、积分、极限"></a>求和、积分、极限</h2><table><thead><tr><th>符号</th><th>LaTeX 代码</th><th>示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>∑</td><td><code>\sum</code></td><td><code>\sum_{i=1}^n i^2</code>&nbsp;→ $\sum_{i=1}^n i^2$</td></tr><tr><td>∫</td><td><code>\int</code></td><td><code>\int_{a}^{b} x^2 \, dx</code>&nbsp;→ $\int_{a}^{b} x^2 , dx$</td></tr><tr><td>lim</td><td><code>\lim</code></td><td><code>\lim_{x \to \infty} f(x)</code>&nbsp;→ $\lim_{x \to \infty} f(x)$</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="补充"><a href="#补充" class="headerlink" title="补充"></a>补充</h2><p>$\infty$ ： <code>\infty</code></p><h1 id="高级数学表达式"><a href="#高级数学表达式" class="headerlink" title="高级数学表达式"></a>高级数学表达式</h1><h2 id="上下标"><a href="#上下标" class="headerlink" title="上下标"></a>上下标</h2><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span>x<span class="built_in">^</span>2 + y<span class="built_in">^</span>{n+1} = z<span class="built_in">_</span>{ij}<span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>效果：$x^2 + y^{n+1} = z_{ij}$</p><h2 id="分式"><a href="#分式" class="headerlink" title="分式"></a>分式</h2><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\frac</span>{a}{b}<span class="built_in">$</span> 或 <span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\dfrac</span>{a}{b}<span class="built_in">$</span> (显示大小)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\frac</span>{x+1}{x-1}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>效果：$\frac{a}{b}$ 和 $\dfrac{a}{b}$</p><p>$$<br>\frac{x+1}{x-1}<br>$$</p><h2 id="根式"><a href="#根式" class="headerlink" title="根式"></a>根式</h2><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>{x}<span class="built_in">$</span>  <span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>[n]{x}<span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>{<span class="keyword">\frac</span>{a}{b}}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>效果：$\sqrt{x}$ 和 $\sqrt[n]{x}$</p><p>$$<br>\sqrt{\frac{a}{b}}<br>$$</p><h2 id="矩阵"><a href="#矩阵" class="headerlink" title="矩阵"></a>矩阵</h2><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>{matrix}</span><br><span class="line">a <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> b <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">c <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> d </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>{matrix}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>{bmatrix}</span><br><span class="line">1 <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> 2 <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">3 <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> 4</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>{bmatrix}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>{pmatrix}</span><br><span class="line">x <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> y <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">z <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> w</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>{pmatrix}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{matrix}<br>a &amp; b \<br>c &amp; d<br>\end{matrix}<br>$$</p><p>$$<br>\begin{bmatrix}<br>1 &amp; 2 \<br>3 &amp; 4<br>\end{bmatrix}<br>$$</p><p>$$<br>\begin{pmatrix}<br>x &amp; y \<br>z &amp; w<br>\end{pmatrix}<br>$$</p><h2 id="多行公式"><a href="#多行公式" class="headerlink" title="多行公式"></a>多行公式</h2><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>{align}</span><br><span class="line">f(x) <span class="built_in">&amp;</span>= (x+1)<span class="built_in">^</span>2 <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="built_in">&amp;</span>= x<span class="built_in">^</span>2 + 2x + 1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>{align}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>$$<br>\begin{align}<br>f(x) &amp;= (x+1)^2 \<br>     &amp;= x^2 + 2x + 1<br>\end{align}<br>$$</p><h1 id="实用技巧"><a href="#实用技巧" class="headerlink" title="实用技巧"></a>实用技巧</h1><ol><li><strong>公式编号</strong>：</li></ol><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line">e<span class="built_in">^</span>{i<span class="keyword">\pi</span>} + 1 = 0 <span class="keyword">\tag</span>{1}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>$$<br>e^{i\pi} + 1 = 0 \tag{1}<br>$$</p><ol start="2"><li><strong>条件表达式</strong>：</li></ol><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br><span class="line">f(n) = </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>{cases} </span><br><span class="line">n/2 <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\text</span>{如果 } n <span class="keyword">\text</span>{ 是偶数} <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">3n+1 <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\text</span>{如果 } n <span class="keyword">\text</span>{ 是奇数}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>{cases}</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>$$<br>f(n) =<br>\begin{cases}<br>n/2 &amp; \text{如果 } n \text{ 是偶数} \<br>3n+1 &amp; \text{如果 } n \text{ 是奇数}<br>\end{cases}<br>$$</p><ol start="3"><li><strong>化学方程式</strong>（需要 mhchem 扩展）：</li></ol><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\ce</span>{H2O}<span class="built_in">$</span>  <span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\ce</span>{SO4<span class="built_in">^</span>2-}<span class="built_in">$</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>$\ce{H2O}$  $\ce{SO4^2-}$</p><ol start="4"><li><strong>引用公式</strong>（结合 Obsidian 的笔记链接功能）：</li></ol><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">如公式 [[#^eq1]] 所示...</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br><span class="line">E=mc^2 \label{eq1} ^eq1</span><br><span class="line">$$</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p>$$<br>E=mc^2 \label{eq1} ^eq1<br>$$</p><h1 id="高级用法"><a href="#高级用法" class="headerlink" title="高级用法"></a>高级用法</h1><h2 id="箭头"><a href="#箭头" class="headerlink" title="箭头"></a>箭头</h2><ul><li><p><code>\to</code>&nbsp;→ $\to$</p></li><li><p><code>\Rightarrow</code>&nbsp;→ $\Rightarrow$</p></li><li><p><code>\Leftrightarrow</code>&nbsp;→ $\Leftrightarrow$</p></li></ul><h2 id="导数"><a href="#导数" class="headerlink" title="导数"></a>导数</h2><ul><li><p><code>f'(x)</code>&nbsp;→ $f’(x)$</p></li><li><p><code>\frac{dy}{dx}</code>&nbsp;→ $\frac{dy}{dx}$</p></li></ul><h2 id="概率统计"><a href="#概率统计" class="headerlink" title="概率统计"></a>概率统计</h2><ul><li><p><code>P(A)</code>&nbsp;→ $P(A)$</p></li><li><p><code>\mathbb{E}[X]</code>&nbsp;→ $\mathbb{E}[X]$</p></li><li><p><code>\sigma^2</code>&nbsp;→ $\sigma^2$</p></li></ul><h2 id="逻辑符号"><a href="#逻辑符号" class="headerlink" title="逻辑符号"></a>逻辑符号</h2><ul><li><p><code>\forall</code>&nbsp;→ $\forall$</p></li><li><p><code>\exists</code>&nbsp;→ $\exists$</p></li><li><p><code>\neg</code>&nbsp;→ $\neg$</p></li></ul><h1 id="常见问题解决"><a href="#常见问题解决" class="headerlink" title="常见问题解决"></a>常见问题解决</h1><ol><li><p><strong>公式不渲染</strong>：</p><ul><li>确保在设置中启用了数学公式渲染</li><li>检查美元符号是否配对</li><li>避免在公式中使用特殊字符（如未转义的_）</li></ul></li><li><p><strong>空格不显示</strong>：</p><ul><li>使用 <code>\,</code>, <code>\:</code>, <code>\;</code> 等空格命令</li><li>或者使用 <code>\text{ }</code> 包裹空格：<code>$a\text{ }b$</code></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>字体样式</strong>：</p><ul><li>粗体：<code>\mathbf{x}</code> → $\mathbf{x}$</li><li>斜体：<code>\mathit{x}</code> → $\mathit{x}$</li><li>黑板粗体：<code>\mathbb{R}</code> → $\mathbb{R}$</li></ul></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
